If you want to get the data of  a specific dimension, you can use it as follows, with the [doc](https://www.echartsjs.com/option.html#series-bar.label.formatter): 
```js
series: [
        {
            type: 'bar',
            label: {
                show: true,
                formatter: '{b}: {@2015}'
            }
        }]
```

New design:
![](http://g.recordit.co/F3roUnkJ9a.gif)

`formatter` can contain DOM like:

```js
formatter: function (param) {
  return '<div>' + param.title + '</div><div class="triangle"></div>';
}
```

